its leveling from 1 to 61. the 6 hours is just for show, the levels show the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>   real</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> investment of time and dedication.<br>
<br>
a level is a relative rank, and is a easily measured unit of a players personal investment of time and dedication. the mage epic can be obtained, irrigardless of time investment or dedication. the mage epic can be obtained with a few k plat from ebay.<br>
sure some people spend as much time on their epic, as they did leveling. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>most people do not</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. most people who got their epics, including myself, just GOT LUCKY in hate, and then threw some plat around to finish various parts up (come on, dont tell me most of you epic mages didnt at least buy your cloak :P).<br>
