<br>
Senario:<br>
There are hard mobs that epic pets can't tank and mobs will eat epic pet alive.  PoP mobs hit hard.<br>
<br>
Solution 1:<br>
- Raise Epic pet to do uber damage and have higher HP.<br>
Result:<br>
- 50ish Epiced mage can have comparable power with 65 none epiced mage.  <br>
<br>
Solution 2:<br>
- Leave Epic alone and have less powerful 61+ pet than epic.<br>
Result:<br>
- Epic pet will not scale up with PoP level mobs and we will be underpowered compare to other classes.<br>
<br>
Solution 3:<br>
- Make the new pet stronger than Epic.<br>
Result:<br>
- Many epiced mages will get pissed (mostly, due to the pride).<br>
But Mages will be able to to scale up with PoP mobs.<br>
<br>
I choose solution 3.<br>
<br>
Question:  What do we do with epic pet if 61+ pets are stronger than epic?<br>
Answer: Make epic quest 2.0.  THE ONLY WAY.<br>
<br>
Do NOT REFUSE MORE POWER.<br>
